            <h2>Intermediate Level </h2>
            <h3 id="baslikortala">The Unforgettable Summer Camp</h3>
            <p>In the small town of Greenridge, where hills rolled and the sun painted the sky in hues of orange, a group of teenagers eagerly anticipated the highlight of their summer&mdash;the Greenridge Adventure Camp.</p>

            <p>The camp was nestled at the edge of Whispering Woods, and this year, it promised an unforgettable experience. Among the excited campers were Sarah, a nature enthusiast with a passion for photography, and Jake, an adventurous soul with a knack for telling ghost stories.</p>

            <p>As they arrived at the campsite, the air buzzed with anticipation. Tents were pitched, and the campfire was lit. The camp director, Mr. Thompson, a wise man with a beard as white as the moon, welcomed everyone.</p>

            <p>The first day was filled with team-building activities. Sarah&#39;s team won the scavenger hunt, finding hidden treasures in the woods, while Jake&#39;s team excelled in a daring high ropes course. That evening, under the starlit sky, they gathered around the campfire for a storytelling session.</p>

            <p>As Jake began his spooky tale, rustling sounds echoed through the woods. Suddenly, a mysterious figure emerged&mdash;Old Man Harrison, the legendary explorer believed to have discovered Whispering Woods decades ago.</p>

            <p>Old Man Harrison shared tales of hidden caves and secret paths, sparking curiosity among the teenagers. The next day, Sarah and Jake decided to embark on their own adventure, following the clues left by the old explorer.</p>

            <p>Their journey led them through dense forests and babbling brooks. Along the way, they encountered unique wildlife and discovered the entrance to a hidden cave. Inside, they found ancient drawings depicting the history of Greenridge and the magic that Whispering Woods held.</p>

            <p>Excitement bubbled within them as they stumbled upon a chest filled with old maps. The maps revealed the location of a long-forgotten tree, said to grant wishes to those who found it. Determined, Sarah and Jake set out to locate the magical tree.</p>

            <p>Their quest tested their friendship and problem-solving skills, but they persevered. Finally, as the sun set on the last day of camp, they discovered the enchanted tree. With a shared wish for everlasting friendship and unforgettable adventures, they touched the tree, feeling a surge of magic in the air.</p>

            <p>As they returned to camp, the once mysterious Whispering Woods seemed to embrace them with a warm breeze, whispering secrets of gratitude. The camp ended, but the memories lingered, turning that summer into a cherished chapter in the book of their lives.</p>

            <p>And so, the teenagers left Greenridge Adventure Camp with a newfound appreciation for friendship, the magic of nature, and the thrill of exploration. As they waved goodbye, the hills echoed with laughter, and the sun painted the sky in hues of gratitude. The end.</p>



